## New Project: xmlguard
- **Replaces:** defusedxml (Python, 150M downloads/month, 537 stars)
- **Why:** Last stable release March 2021 (5+ years). 0.8.0rc2 unreleased since Sept 2023. Single maintainer (Christian Heimes) largely inactive. Officially recommended in Python docs but not updated. No forks with traction. Classifiers only declare Python 2.7-3.9.
- **Package:** xmlguard (verified available on PyPI)
- **Improvements:** Python 3.10-3.13+ support, full type annotations, configurable limits, defusedxml compat layer, XInclude blocking
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #643 (scaffolding), #644 (core parsers), #645 (xmlrpc/lxml), #646 (compat layer), #647 (test suite)

